# runs directory — pipeline output is auto-generated here

Each pipeline run creates a subdirectory named by run ID containing:
  - state.json           Full serialized RunState (all proposals, critiques, traces)
  - latest_proposal.md   Final proposal in Markdown
  - traces.jsonl         Per-agent observability traces (JSONL)
  - pipeline.log         Human-readable structured log
  - summary.json         Quick-reference summary (run_id, status, cost, score)

This directory is tracked in git (via this .gitkeep) but individual run files are gitignored.
